BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 93.12 600 Td (Chapter 1: Why Budgeting Matters) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (A budget is simply a plan for how you will spend your money each month.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Without a budget, money disappears and you wonder where it all went.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Budgeting is not about restriction. It is about giving yourself permission.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (When you budget, you decide in advance what matters most to you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Studies show that people who budget save three times more than those who do not.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (A budget reduces financial stress and arguments about money in relationships.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (It helps you avoid debt by ensuring you spend less than you earn.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Budgeting gives you clarity about your true financial situation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (You cannot build wealth without knowing where your money goes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Even high-income earners go broke without a spending plan.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (A budget is your roadmap to financial goals like retirement or a home.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (The good news: budgeting is simple once you learn the basic principles.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (1) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
