BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 66.24000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 6: Cutting Unnecessary Spending) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Cancel subscriptions you have not used in the last thirty days.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Negotiate your phone, internet, and insurance bills. Call and ask for discounts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Cook at home more often. Restaurant meals cost five times more than homemade.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Use the 24-hour rule: wait a day before any purchase over fifty dollars.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Unsubscribe from marketing emails that tempt you to buy things you do not need.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Switch to generic brands for groceries, medicine, and cleaning products.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Use the library instead of buying books, magazines, and movies.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Carpool, bike, or use public transit to reduce transportation costs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Make coffee at home instead of buying five-dollar drinks daily.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Shop with a list and stick to it to avoid impulse purchases.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Find free entertainment: parks, hiking, community events, and free museums.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Small daily savings of five dollars add up to over eighteen hundred per year.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (6) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
